summary:
In 2014, I completed a 3-course Graduate Certificate in Serious Game Design and Research through Michigan State University&rsquo;s College of Communication Arts and Sciences. Here I offer a bit of my experience in each course.
The &ldquo;TC&rdquo; before the course number stands for &ldquo;Telecommunications,&rdquo; the old department name in the College of Communication Arts and Sciences before they changed it to &ldquo;Media and Information.&rdquo;
TC 831: Theories of Games and Interaction for Design Fall 2012
